1.   DEFINITIONS AND INTERPRETATION
1.1  In this Agreement unless the context otherwise requires the following words
     shall have the following meaning:

"AFFILIATES"       means any company, corporation, partnership, joint venture or other entity designated as such by XFN;
"CONTENT"          means economic news including articles, reports, data, information and such materials that CEIS deems appropriate for distribution, regardless of whether it aligns with Schedule 1;
